## 🎯 TIER S — High value, low cost (next session priorities)

### [ ] Phase 18 — Decision Journal + Error Analysis (2-3h)
- Nouvelle table `decisions` : (id, ts, ticker, decision_type, thesis_id, confidence_pre, reasoning, regime_snapshot, credit_snapshot, materiality_snapshot, outcome_30d, outcome_90d, outcome_resolved_at, mistakes_tags)
- decision_type ∈ {entry, scale_in, partial_exit, full_exit, override, no_action_flag}
- Cmd `/journal <ticker> <type> <confidence> <reasoning>` → log entry
- Cron J+30 et J+90 : auto-resolve outcome via price delta + classify mistake
- Cmd `/journal_review` : top mistakes par regime / par decision_type / par ticker class
- ROI : direct hit sur biais asymétrique PLTR/NVDA → mesure empirique du "sell too early"
- Prérequis : aucun (peut tourner même sans positions réelles)

### [ ] Phase 19 — Narrative Saturation Detector (2-3h)
- Nouvelle table `narrative_state` : (narrative, ts, signal_count_30d, polarity_avg, insider_polarity_inverse, media_saturation_score, composite 0-1)
- Cron quotidien : agrège signals.narratives JSON par narrative active
- Score composite = signal_count_30d × |polarity_avg| × (1 - insider_alignment)
- Cmd `/narrative` : top 5 narratives par saturation
- Trigger alert quand narrative_saturation >0.8 + insider_distribution + credit TIGHT
- ROI : détection late-stage automatique vs intuition

### [ ] Phase 20 — Regime Transition Detector (1-2h)
- Nouvelle table `regime_history` : snapshot quotidien de get_regime() + get_credit_regime() + breadth metrics
- Helper `detect_regime_transition(window_days=14)` : compare T vs T-14j sur N inputs (HY OAS, yield curve, breadth, leadership)
- Flag quand ≥3 inputs basculent en simultané
- Cmd `/regime_delta` : diff lisible 14j
- Notification Telegram dédiée si transition détectée
- ROI : edge réel vs snapshot statique du régime actuel

