### [x] Phase 25a — Enrich /analyze with comprehensive fundamentals — DONE 2026-05-12 morning
17 new yfinance fields populated: EBITDA absolu + margin, OCF/FCF absolu, ROE/ROA, D/E ratio, current/quick ratio, PEG, short interest (% float + days-to-cover), insider/institutional ownership %, revenue CAGR multi-year, earnings growth QoQ. Validated empirically on NVDA: LLM cite explicitement ROE 101.5% / D/E 0.07x / PEG 0.68 / OCF-FCF spread = capex inference.

### [ ] Phase 25b — Structured JSON output + self-consistency (1-1.5h)
- Force LLM response en JSON strict: {score_0_100, bull_args:[], bear_args:[], probability_bull:0-1, key_risks:[], synthesis_md}
- Self-consistency: 3 LLM calls même prompt, vote majoritaire sur score, médiane sur probability
- Coût: 3x ($0.12/call) compensé par cache 24h
- Bénéfice: outputs parsables + variance réduite + comparabilité entre /analyze

